 Ordering &amp; Dedicated Support</b> – Enjoy a hassle-free process with priority assistance.</li>\n          <li>\n<b>Early Access to New Releases</b> – Stay ahead with exclusive product launches.</li>\n          <li>\n<b>Low Minimum Orders &amp; Scalable Solutions</b> – Perfect for both small practices and larger clinics.</li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"siv-fp-card\">\n        <h2 class=\"siv-fp-cardh\">Who can apply?</h2>\n        <p class=\"siv-fp-lead\">Our wholesale program is open to:</p>\n        <ul class=\"siv-fp-list\">\n          <li><b>Licensed Aestheticians &amp; Skincare Professionals</b></li>\n          <li>Med-Spas, Clinics, and Private Practices</li>\n          <li>Doctors, Physicians, and Medical Specialists</li>\n          <li>Chiropractors, Physical Therapists &amp; Wellness Practitioners</li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"siv-fp-foot\">\n      <p>Fill out the form below to verify your credentials and gain access to exclusive pricing and benefits. Our team will review your application and respond shortly.</p>\n      <a class=\"siv-fp-btn\" href=\"https://sivcare.com/pages/wholesale-enquiry\">Apply</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
